author: WCAX News
title: Candidates continue to stump in New Hampshire
text:
WEST LEBANON, N.H. - Hillary Clinton will be campaigning in New Hampshire next weekend. Meanwhile republican candidate and Ohio Governor John Kasich will host a town hall in West Lebanon on Wednesday.
That's one of five events he will hold in the coming days.
Donald Trump continues to lead the GOP field.
